text: Marwan Pablo or Marwan Ahmed Motawea (born May 24, 1995), previously known as Dama, is an Egyptian rapper and hip-hop artist from Cairo. He was influenced by the genre of Hip Hop. He is best known for Free, Ghaba, El Gemeza, Sindbad, Barbary and more. ==References== Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:People from Cairo Category:Egyptian singers Category:Hip hop singers
